@startuml
title Viaverse Business Account Onboarding — Sequence Diagram

actor Owner
participant "Client / Business UI" as Client
participant "API Gateway / BFF" as BFF
participant "business-service" as Business
participant "identity-service" as Identity
participant "media-service" as Media
participant "billing/payment-service" as Billing
participant "search-service" as Search
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

Owner -> Client : create business
Client -> BFF : POST /businesses
BFF -> Business : createBusiness(command)
Business -> Identity : grant/check OPERATE_BUSINESS capability
Business -> Media : attach logo/photos mediaIds
Business -> Billing : create trial/subscription profile
Business -> Business : publish-ready policy
Business -> Search : index public business projection
Business -> Kafka : BusinessCreated / BusinessPublished
Business --> BFF : business status DTO
BFF --> Client : render onboarding progress

note bottom
business-service owns business profile/branches/catalog.
Identity owns account/capability.
Billing owns plan/subscription.
Search owns public projection.
end note
@enduml
